Pre-reqs: You need numpy and scipy.
Follow instructions from here: http://www.scipy.org/Installing_SciPy/Mac_OS_X
 git clone https://github.com/numpy/numpy.git
 git clone https://github.com/scipy/scipy.git
 virtualenv /tmp/sklearn
 source /tmp/sklearn/bin/activate
 cd numpy
 python setup.py build
 python setup.py install
 cd ../scipy
 python setup.py build
 python setup.py install

cd scikit-learn
python setup.py install
python setup.py register -r chishop sdist upload -r chishop
